com.github.triceo.splitlog.api

Interface MidDeliveryMessageCondition


  • public interface MidDeliveryMessageCondition
    Allows users to filter messages based on their own criteria. These conditions will be used whenever the LogWatch and its Followers need to notify other parts of code about newly received Messages.
